text: We experienced a bad service today by the aunty. As a beginner, we need her guidance and sharing what to buy, but with her attitude of unprofessional and not friendly made us had an unpleasant shopping time. Will not recommend this place!

Excellent shop. sells many types of high end fishing lures from manafacturers like Yo Zuri , terminal fishing tackle (hooks, lines sinkers, etc.) , and rods (Multipliers, Spincasting,etc.). sells many fishing accessories also. sells excellent squid/ cuttlefish Egi Lures, featuring imported japanese brands like yamashita.

Good service
Fair price.
Stock a bit limited due to store size.
